{"tid":724833,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"成日都唔開心愚蠢既人類阿 睇完呢個應該會開心返","createTime":"2018-07-01T08:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T06:29:08.000Z","uid":104422,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"72011a3efaf769bdc60f8b06111882411ce94e3d","tid":724833,"uid":104422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:45:35.000Z","msg":"登登登櫈<br />\n<br />\n就係My Hero Academia啦!<br />\n<br />\n等自己可以忘記一下傷心既環境同煩惱<br />\n叉滿電先再出發!<br />\n<br />\n佢熱血<br />\n佢搞笑<br />\n佢感人<br />\n精彩既劇情會令你既煩惱一掃而空!<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/163931_06689e928e0f62229848df31055a6e9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F163931_06689e928e0f62229848df31055a6e9c.jpg&h=fa50da33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/163932_704b27084030f0e97ce3ce3e5953e9e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F163932_704b27084030f0e97ce3ce3e5953e9e5.jpg&h=5ec1f724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/163932_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F163932_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg&h=593b14ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/163933_f78492f0513c659e69dab2e47f567202.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F163933_f78492f0513c659e69dab2e47f567202.gif&h=b595d02f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊度有得睇?<br />\n係google打ebb會搵到可以睇既方法<br />\n<br />\n如果想要更多介紹<br />\n可以睇我岩岩整既介紹片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vWIeb8iQndA&amp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvWIeb8iQndA%26&d=ooyHLuA5Vpqq1UGCPGe%2BRgdLCpCjoNGxX